{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "{{collection_id}}",
    "name": "{{api_name}} - Documentação",
    "description": "# {{api_name}}\n\n## Visão Geral\n\n{{description}}\n\n## Serviços Incluídos\n\n- {{services}}\n\n## URLs Base\n\n- Desenvolvimento: `{{dev_url}}`\n- Produção: `{{prod_url}}`\n\n## Autenticação\n\n{{auth_type}}: JWT (Bearer Token)\n\n- Endpoint de login: `POST /auth/login`\n- Endpoint de refresh: `POST /auth/refresh`\n\n## Status\n\n- ✅ Em desenvolvimento\n- ✅ Documentação completa",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Authentication",
      "description": "Endpoints de autenticação JWT",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST /auth/login",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{user_email}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{user_password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "## Login\n\n### Validações\n- email (string): Obrigatório → 422: \"Email is required\"\n- password (string): Obrigatório → 422: \"Password is required\"\n\n### Regras de Negócio\n- Credenciais devem estar corretas\n- Usuário deve estar ativo\n- Token válido por 24h (access_token)\n- Refresh token válido por 7 dias\n\n### Erros\n- 422: Email/Password ausente\n- 401: Credenciais inválidas\n- 403: Usuário inativo"
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Login successful\", function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "let res = pm.response.json();",
                  "",
                  "if (res.access_token) {",
                  "    pm.environment.set('auth_token', res.access_token);",
                  "}",
                  "",
                  "if (res.refresh_token) {",
                  "    pm.environment.set('refresh_token', res.refresh_token);",
                  "}",
                  "",
                  "if (res.expires_in) {",
                  "    let expiresAt = Date.now() + (res.expires_in * 1000);",
                  "    pm.environment.set('auth_expires_at', expiresAt);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "✅ Sucesso",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"test@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/login",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["auth", "login"]
                }
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [
                {
                  "key": "Content-Type",
                  "value": "application/json"
                }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"access_token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...\",\n  \"refresh_token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...\",\n  \"expires_in\": 86400\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "❌ 422 - Email ausente",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
